za)</city><country>IT</country></address></addressbook></assignee><assignee><addressbook><last-name>Mainetti</last-name><first-name>Mario</first-name><role>05</role><address><city>Valdagno (Vicenza)</city><country>IT</country></address></addressbook></assignee></assignees></us-bibliographic-data-application><abstract id="abstract"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">A crown-type sizer for mounting on a hanger includes a body and a hook extending from a mid-point of the body. The sizer includes a pair of parallel walls and a pair of non-parallel walls, each wall of the non-parallel walls being joined to each wall of the parallel walls, the pairs of walls defining a lower open base and an open base in an upper part of the sizer for passing over the hook. Each of the parallel walls has a single boss disposed in a corner of the respective parallel wall and each non-parallel wall is shorter in height than at least one parallel wall.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>